sorna-common
============

|PyPI version| |Python Versions| |Build Status| |Code Coverage|

Common libraries and utilities for Sorna

Installation
------------

.. code:: sh

    pip install sorna-common

For development
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

.. code:: sh

    pip install -r requirements-dev.txt

